message: “We walk among you with scars so deep that you don’t even see,” Daniels told a group gathered Thursday at the Women’s Leadership Summit to discuss human trafficking and the local efforts to curb it and help victims. “We have dreams and aspirations. We want to be just like you. We just want to be normal.”

data.description: Holly Daniels may not seem so different from her fellow Columbus State Community College students. She works hard at school, makes the Dean’s List,
data.title: 'We just want to be normal,' human trafficking survivor says
